OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Corchestrating brutal killing of love
OL,5,Crival
OL,7,FA drug dealer who meticulously planned
OL,8,Fand carried out the horrific murder of
OL,9,Fhis ex-partner's new lover now faces a
OL,10,Flife sentence after being convicted of
OL,11,Fmurder.
OL,13,FJohn Belfield, 31, led a calculated
OL,14,Fattack on 38-year-old Thomas Campbell,
OL,15,Fwho had started a relationship with
OL,16,FBelfield's former partner, Demi-Lee
OL,17,FDriver.
