OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Corchestrating brutal killing of love
OL,5,Crival
OL,7,FManchester Crown Court heard how
OL,8,FBelfield recruited accomplices,
OL,9,Fcarried out surveillance, and launched
OL,10,Fa brutal ambush that left Campbell
OL,11,Fdead in his own home.
OL,13,FOn the night of 2 July 2022, Belfield
OL,14,Fand two other men lay in wait outside
OL,15,FCampbell's home on Riverside in
OL,16,FMossley, Tameside. The court was told
OL,17,Fthat the killing came after a week of
OL,18,Ftargeted surveillance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
