OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Corchestrating brutal killing of love
OL,5,Crival
OL,7,FCampbell had been followed, a tracking
OL,8,Fdevice was secretly placed on his car
OL,9,Fwhile he was on the school run, and a
OL,10,Fprevious attempt to attack him had
OL,11,Fbeen aborted.
OL,13,FWhen the attack finally went ahead,
OL,14,FCampbell was ambushed on his driveway
OL,15,Fand dragged inside. What followed was
OL,16,Ftwo hours of torture.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
