OL,5,Crival
OL,7,FThe court heard how he was stabbed,
OL,8,Fstrangled, and had boiling liquid
OL,9,Fpoured over his genitals. He suffered
OL,10,F61 separate injuries. Prosecutors
OL,11,Fdescribed his death as a case of being
OL,12,F"tortured to death".
OL,14,FA major police investigation later
OL,15,Frevealed Campbell's ex-wife, Coleen
OL,16,FCampbell, had been complicit in the
OL,17,Fplot.
