OL,7,FShe had provided Belfield's group with
OL,8,Fkey information about her former
OL,9,Fhusband's movements and whereabouts `
OL,10,Feven involving her own daughter to
OL,11,Fconfirm his address. The couple, who
OL,12,Fshared two children, had divorced in
OL,13,F2019 after ten years together.
OL,15,FIn 2023, Coleen Campbell was convicted
OL,16,Fof manslaughter for her role in the
OL,17,Fattack and sentenced to 13 years in
OL,18,Fprison.
