OL,5,Crival
OL,7,FReece Steven, one of the attackers
OL,8,FBelfield recruited, was found guilty
OL,9,Fof murder and sentenced to life with a
OL,10,Fminimum term of 37 years.
OL,12,FAnother man, Stephen Cleworth ` who
OL,13,Fhad helped plant the tracker but did
OL,14,Fnot take part in the killing as he was
OL,15,Fat a swingers' club on the night ` was
OL,16,Fconvicted of manslaughter and
OL,17,Fsentenced to life with a minimum of 12
OL,18,Fyears. All three were also found
OL,19,Fguilty of conspiracy to rob.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
