OL,5,Crival
OL,7,FThe identity of the third attacker
OL,8,Fremains unknown and he is still wanted
OL,9,Fby police.
OL,11,FBelfield, however, managed to flee the
OL,12,FUK just two days after the killing. He
OL,13,Feventually travelled to Suriname in
OL,14,FSouth America, where he stayed with a
OL,15,Fcousin who was also on the run. He was
OL,16,Farrested there in March 2023 and
OL,17,Fextradited to the UK a year later.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
