OL,5,Crival
OL,7,FDuring his trial, Belfield claimed he
OL,8,Fhad agreed with Steven and Cleworth to
OL,9,Frob Campbell, believing he had hidden
OL,10,Fdrugs in remote locations across
OL,11,FTameside and east Manchester.
OL,13,FHe alleged Coleen Campbell had
OL,14,Fprovided suggestions on where the
OL,15,Fdrugs might be. Belfield denied
OL,16,Fwanting to harm Campbell and dismissed
OL,17,Fsuggestions of jealousy over the new
OL,18,Frelationship.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
