OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Corchestrating brutal killing of love
OL,5,Crival
OL,7,FBut after a four-week trial, a jury
OL,8,Ffound Belfield unanimously guilty of
OL,9,Fboth murder and conspiracy to rob. He
OL,10,Fnow awaits sentencing and is expected
OL,11,Fto receive a significant minimum term.
OL,13,FDetective Sergeant Paul Davies of
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police, who led the
OL,15,Finvestigation, expressed relief that
OL,16,FBelfield had finally been brought to
OL,17,Fjustice in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
