OL,7,F"I wanted to get him back and see him
OL,8,Fin court, not over there," he said. "I
OL,9,Fwanted him to be brought back here and
OL,10,Fface justice."
OL,12,FHe praised Thomas Campbell's family
OL,13,Ffor their support and composure
OL,14,Fthroughout the investigation.
OL,16,F"All the while, you've the family who
OL,17,Fyou're speaking to, who knew he was in
OL,18,Fcustody (in Suriname). The (Campbell)
OL,19,Ffamily were brilliant," he added.
